Come on, let's go.

58:06.916 --> 58:08.918
(Gunfire)

59:29.133 --> 59:31.802
Hey, look.
There's an old guy
on the bridge.

59:42.780 --> 59:45.115
Hey, mister.
What the hell are you
doing out here?

59:45.149 --> 59:47.718
Hey hey!
Stand back!

59:47.752 --> 59:50.954
These birds are contagious.
Now go away.

59:54.057 --> 59:56.360
Hey, I thought I told
you to stand back.

59:56.392 --> 59:58.095
These birds are
contaminated.

59:58.128 --> 01:00:00.097
They have bird flu virus.

01:00:00.130 --> 01:00:01.766
Now go away.

01:00:01.799 --> 01:00:05.001
Could we just talk about it
at the picnic area?

01:00:05.035 --> 01:00:07.904
You want to talk?
Okay.

01:00:07.938 --> 01:00:09.940
All right.
We'll talk.

01:00:24.421 --> 01:00:26.956
(Kids laughing)

01:00:26.991 --> 01:00:28.825
Guys, this is
Dr. Jones.

01:00:28.859 --> 01:00:30.026
How do you do?

01:00:30.059 --> 01:00:32.162
- Hi.
- Hi.

01:00:32.196 --> 01:00:36.734
Sir, don't you know
that these birds are
attacking people?

01:00:36.767 --> 01:00:38.034
- These birds?
- Yes.

01:00:38.067 --> 01:00:41.171
No way.
They're dead from
the bird flu virus.

01:00:41.205 --> 01:00:43.407
- Bird flu virus?
- How do you know this?

01:00:43.439 --> 01:00:45.441
I just tested their blood.

01:00:45.474 --> 01:00:47.177
Then why are they
attacking us?

01:00:47.211 --> 01:00:49.747
I don't know.

01:00:49.780 --> 01:00:53.049
But what I do know
is global warming is
causing viral diseases

01:00:53.082 --> 01:00:56.721
Such as bird flu,
west nile virus and SARS.

01:00:56.754 --> 01:00:57.855
So what are you saying?

01:00:57.887 --> 01:01:00.424
That global warming is causing
these birds to attack?

01:01:00.456 --> 01:01:02.058
No.

01:01:02.091 --> 01:01:05.061
I'm a scientist...
An ornithologist.

01:01:05.095 --> 01:01:08.898
I can't state any scientific
fact without evidence.

01:01:08.933 --> 01:01:11.736
But there is scientific
evidence to show

01:01:11.768 --> 01:01:13.770
That because of our
burning of fossil fuels

01:01:13.803 --> 01:01:15.072
And creating
greenhouse gasses

01:01:15.104 --> 01:01:17.074
Which is causing
global warming,

01:01:17.106 --> 01:01:19.076
It's raising the temperature
of the seas

01:01:19.108 --> 01:01:21.746
And species like
the krill are dying.

01:01:21.779 --> 01:01:25.182
So many bird species
can't find food

01:01:25.215 --> 01:01:26.883
Like the neritic
krill.

01:01:26.917 --> 01:01:29.018
They eventually
starve and die,

01:01:29.053 --> 01:01:30.921
Wash up on the shore.

01:01:30.954 --> 01:01:33.122
There's also evidence
that global warming

01:01:33.156 --> 01:01:35.960
Is interrupting the birth,
mating and migration cycles

01:01:35.992 --> 01:01:37.828
Of many species.

01:01:37.862 --> 01:01:40.029
In fact,
in the last few years

01:01:40.063 --> 01:01:42.867
40 species have become extinct
because of global warming.

01:01:44.268 --> 01:01:47.003
However, there is
interesting research

01:01:47.036 --> 01:01:49.273
That in prehistoric times

01:01:49.306 --> 01:01:51.140
Birds did attack cavemen.

01:01:51.174 --> 01:01:54.845
They used to claw
at their eyes and skull.

01:01:54.879 --> 01:01:57.513
They'd either leave them
for dead or then come back

01:01:57.546 --> 01:01:59.115
Because their injuries
were so bad

01:01:59.148 --> 01:02:01.718
And finally
finish off the kill.

01:02:05.054 --> 01:02:06.990
If they attack me,

01:02:07.023 --> 01:02:09.493
I've got a little
present for them.

01:02:09.525 --> 01:02:12.261
Well, you certainly know
a lot about birds.

01:02:13.830 --> 01:02:16.165
Well, I should.
I'm an ornithologist.

01:02:16.200 --> 01:02:19.002
I study and work with birds
for a living.

01:02:19.036 --> 01:02:21.004
You should come with us.
It's safer.

01:02:21.038 --> 01:02:23.774
I don't need protection.
I can take care of myself.

01:02:23.808 --> 01:02:26.009
I've got my truck
and my trailer.

01:02:26.043 --> 01:02:30.179
Besides, I'm not worried
about the blackbirds.

01:02:30.213 --> 01:02:32.817
They're not
the dangerous animal.

01:02:32.850 --> 01:02:35.184
It's the human species
that's the dangerous

01:02:35.218 --> 01:02:37.553
And menacing
and terrifying animal.

01:02:37.586 --> 01:02:40.858
Because of his fossil fuel
related activities,

01:02:40.891 --> 01:02:42.225
He's causing global warming.

01:02:42.259 --> 01:02:44.528
It's killing life
and earth itself.

01:02:45.995 --> 01:02:47.932
It's the human species

01:02:47.965 --> 01:02:50.835
That needs to quit playing
cowboy with nature.

01:02:52.235 --> 01:02:55.071
We must act
more like astronauts,

01:02:55.104 --> 01:02:59.075
Spacemen taking care of
our spaceship earth.

01:03:02.178 --> 01:03:03.780
Well, nice meeting you.

01:03:03.780 --> 01:03:06.215
Good luck.

