01:08:16.160 --> 01:08:18.562
(Screaming, moaning)

01:08:21.465 --> 01:08:24.268
(Moaning continues)

01:08:40.649 --> 01:08:42.652
(Birds screeching)

01:08:42.685 --> 01:08:44.720
(Gunshots)

01:09:06.243 --> 01:09:07.943
I'm going out there
to save them.

01:09:07.977 --> 01:09:09.912
Don't go.
If you go out there
you'll die.

01:09:09.944 --> 01:09:11.515
